WEBVTT

00:00:57.060 --> 00:01:00.725
“Yo! Why dese books neva be about my peoples”

00:01:00.725 --> 00:01:02.890
Yes, I have decided to treat

00:01:02.890 --> 00:01:04.952
all three of my languages as equals

00:01:04.952 --> 00:01:08.950
Because I’m “articulate”

00:01:08.950 --> 00:01:11.371
But who controls articulation?

00:01:11.371 --> 00:01:14.525
Because the English language
is a multifaceted oration

00:01:14.525 --> 00:01:16.344
Subject to indefinite transformation

00:01:16.344 --> 00:01:19.957
Now you may think that it is
ignorant to speak broken English

00:01:19.957 --> 00:01:23.114
But I’m here to tell you that
even “articulate” Americans

00:01:23.114 --> 00:01:25.114
sound foolish to the British

